<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sintu Kumar - About</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo.icon.png" type="image/x-icon" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.1/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-5Hs3dF2AEPkpNAR7UiOHba+lRSJNeM2ECkwxUIxC1Q/FLycGTbNapWXB4tP889k5T5Ju8fs4b1P5z/iB4nMfSQ=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <div class="banner">
      <img src="/images/abut.png" alt="About banner" />
    </div>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="section-title center">About Me</h1>

        <p class="section-text">
          Welcome to my personal website! I'm passionate about exploring the
          world of technology, education, and everything in between. I am
          currently pursuing a <b>Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA)</b> and
          I’m constantly learning new things in programming and software
          development.
        </p>

        <p class="section-text">
          My coding journey is driven by curiosity and a love for problem-solving.
          I enjoy working with different programming languages, taking on coding
          challenges, and building projects that help me grow as a developer.
        </p>

        <p class="section-text">
          Besides studying, I run a YouTube channel,
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Coder_Sintu/shorts" target="_blank"><b>Coder Sintu</b></a>,
          where I share tutorials and educational content to help others learn
          programming and technology in a simple way.
        </p>

        <p class="section-text">
          When I’m not coding, I love watching movies and web series, reading,
          exploring new ideas, and spending time with friends and family.
        </p>

        <div class="cards-grid">
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="icon-circle small">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="card-title">My Interests</h2>
            <p class="section-text small">
              Coding, gaming, learning new technologies, travelling, watching
              movies & web series.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="icon-circle small">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="card-title">My Goal</h2>
            <p class="section-text small">
              To build a strong career in software development and contribute to
              meaningful tech solutions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="icon-circle small">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="card-title">My Vision</h2>
            <p class="section-text small">
              To become a skilled and responsible professional, keep learning,
              and help others grow through education and technology.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
